@startuml Activity_Financial_Monitoring
title Activity Diagram - Financial Monitoring with Geopolitical Context

start
:MarketPanel fetches Yahoo Finance
(BIST 100, BIST 30, BIST Banka,
USDTRY, EURTRY, GBPTRY, gold, oil);
note right: refresh every 2 min

fork
  :Render market panel values and trend arrows;
fork again
  :NewsPanel aggregates ekonomi feeds
  (Bloomberg HT, TCMB, BIST);
  note right: refresh every 5 min
end fork

:User observes TRY depreciation or index drop;

if (Economic news volume spike
or keyword match on takiplistem?) then (yes)
  :Correlate news items with market move;
  :Highlight configured hotspots on map
  (from geo.ts: Ankara, Istanbul, ...);
  :User correlates finance with geopolitics;
else (no)
  :Continue passive monitoring;
endif

stop
@enduml
